      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="7201e-103"><xref:System.Security.AccessControl.DirectorySecurity> 类指定系统目录的访问权限以及访问尝试的审核方式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7201e-103">The <xref:System.Security.AccessControl.DirectorySecurity> class specifies the access rights for a system directory and how access attempts are audited.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7201e-104">此类将访问权限和审核权限表示为一组规则。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7201e-104">This class represents access and audit rights as a set of rules.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7201e-105">每个访问规则由一个 <xref:System.Security.AccessControl.FileSystemAccessRule> 对象表示，而每个审核规则由一个 <xref:System.Security.AccessControl.FileSystemAuditRule> 对象表示。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7201e-105">Each access rule is represented by a <xref:System.Security.AccessControl.FileSystemAccessRule> object, while each audit rule is represented by a <xref:System.Security.AccessControl.FileSystemAuditRule> object.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7201e-106"><xref:System.Security.AccessControl.DirectorySecurity> 类是基础 Windows 文件安全系统的抽象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7201e-106">The <xref:System.Security.AccessControl.DirectorySecurity> class is an abstraction of the underlying Windows file security system.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7201e-107">在此系统中，每个目录都有一个自定义访问控制列表（DACL），用于控制对目录的访问，以及一个系统访问控制列表（SACL），后者指定了审核的访问控制尝试。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7201e-107">In this system, each directory has a discretionary access control list (DACL), which controls access to the directory, and a system access control list (SACL), which specifies the access control attempts that are audited.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7201e-108"><xref:System.Security.AccessControl.FileSystemAccessRule> 和 <xref:System.Security.AccessControl.FileSystemAuditRule> 类是包含 Dacl 和 Sacl 的访问控制项（Ace）的抽象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7201e-108">The <xref:System.Security.AccessControl.FileSystemAccessRule> and <xref:System.Security.AccessControl.FileSystemAuditRule> classes are abstractions of the access control entries (ACEs) that comprise DACLs and SACLs.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7201e-109"><xref:System.Security.AccessControl.DirectorySecurity> 类隐藏了 Dacl 和 Sacl 的许多详细信息;不必担心 ACE 顺序或 null DACL。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7201e-109">The <xref:System.Security.AccessControl.DirectorySecurity> class hides many of the details of DACLs and SACLs; you do not have to worry about ACE ordering or null DACLS.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7201e-110">使用 <xref:System.Security.AccessControl.FileSecurity> 类可检索、添加或更改表示文件的 DACL 和 SACL 的访问规则。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7201e-110">Use the <xref:System.Security.AccessControl.FileSecurity> class to retrieve, add, or change the access rules that represent the DACL and SACL of a file.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7201e-111">下表列出了可以用来访问和维护目录安全性的方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7201e-111">The following tables lists the methods you can use to access and maintain directory security.</span></span>  
  
|<span data-ttu-id="7201e-112">任务</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7201e-112">Task</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="7201e-113">方法</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7201e-113">Methods</span></span>|  
|----------|-------------|  
|<span data-ttu-id="7201e-114">添加规则</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7201e-114">Add rules</span></span>|<xref:System.Security.AccessControl.FileSystemSecurity.AddAccessRule%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType><br /><br /> <xref:System.Security.AccessControl.FileSystemSecurity.AddAuditRule%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="7201e-115">删除规则</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7201e-115">Remove rules</span></span>|<xref:System.Security.AccessControl.FileSystemSecurity.RemoveAccessRule%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType><br /><br /> <xref:System.Security.AccessControl.FileSystemSecurity.RemoveAuditRule%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="7201e-116">检索目录的访问控制</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7201e-116">Retrieve the access control to a directory</span></span>|<xref:System.IO.Directory.GetAccessControl%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType><br /><br /> <xref:System.IO.DirectoryInfo.GetAccessControl%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="7201e-117">将访问控制持久保存到目录</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7201e-117">Persist the access control to a directory</span></span>|<xref:System.IO.Directory.SetAccessControl%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType><br /><br /> <xref:System.IO.DirectoryInfo.SetAccessControl%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>|  
  
   
  
